<h4>
  Types of Particles
</h4>

<p class = 'definition' data-word = 'Alpha Particle (\( \alpha \))'>
  A Helium-4 nucleus
  <br>
  Represented by \( ^4 _2 \text{He} \)
</p>
<p class = 'definition' data-word = 'Beta Particle (\( \beta \))'>
  An electron
  <br>
  Represented by \( ^0 _{-1} \text{e} \)
</p>
<p class = 'Gamma Ray (\( \gamma \))'>
  A very high energy photon (electromagnetic wave)
  <br>
  Represented by \( \gamma \), the Greek letter gamma.
</p>

